    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Xcode 5 下的单元测试]]></title>
    <link href="http://GeforceLee.github.io/blog/2013/11/05/xcode-5-xia-de-dan-yuan-ce-shi/"/>
    <updated>2013-11-05T15:37:00+08:00</updated>
